name: Nystromformer
shortDescription: A TensorFlow/ Keras implementation of Nystromformer, a transformer variant that uses the Nyström method to approximate standard self-attention with O(n) complexity which allows for better scalability.
longDescription: A TensorFlow/ Keras implementation of Nystromformer, a transformer variant that uses the Nyström method to approximate standard self-attention with O(n) complexity which allows for better scalability.
